{
  "stem": "13079.4",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And they found that he had stolen about six million reichsmarks, and the SS court found him guilty and sentenced him to death.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And he was hanged.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And Ilse remained on living in the commandant's quarters at Buchenwald.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And she used to ride horseback and make her rounds on horseback and still exhibiting those things that the good Lord had endowed her with.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And getting ogling from the prisoners and making her reports and mistreatment.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "She also took as house boys young German men and abused them as house boys.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And when she got tired of 'em, she'd send 'em down to the hospital.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And there they were beaten and liquidated, except the last one.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "The last one realized what was happening.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And when Ilse went to Weimar on a shopping spree, he broke every glass in those quarters so when she came back-- and he got drunk.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And while in that drunken stupor, Ilse called up the guard house to come and fetch him.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "Well, that was different from the hospital.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "Ilse's friend was in the hospital.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "He was one of the doctors there and he would dispose of these men when she got tired of 'em.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "Well, she called up the guard house, and they sent two SS men over.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "And they took this guy down to-- this prisoner down to the guard house.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "They beat hell out of him, but he saved his life.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "He didn't go to the hospital.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "They just put him in one of the bunkers there in the guard house.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "And that's how we were able to get a hold of him.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "And he testified against Ilse and, and to some of her habits.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
